Title: Counterstrike
Plot: The Jaffa take the fight to the Ori, using a genocidal weapon on their new worshipers and landing SG-1 in the middle of a war they can't control.
GuestStars: Gary Jones, Tony Amendola, Morena Baccarin, Matthew Glave, Martin Christopher, Shiraine Haas, Aleks Holtz, Sylvesta Stuart, David Andrews, Richard Whiten, Peter Nicholas Smyth
